{"id":198,"parent_id":196,"book_id":2,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":198,"title":"1 Thessalonians 2","subtitle":"","short_title":"1 Thes.","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/2","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 2"],[".studySummary",["i","True ministers preach in a godly manner—Converts are the glory and joy of missionaries."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/2.1","order":"03.15.002.21450"},["b","1"],"For yourselves, brethren, know our",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"entrance"],"in unto you, that it was not in vain:"],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/2.2","order":"03.15.002.21451"},["b","2"],"But even after that we had suffered before, and were shamefully",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"entreated"],", as ye know, at Philippi, we were bold in our God to",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_2b"},"speak"],"unto you the gospel of God with much contention."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/2.3","order":"03.15.002.21452"},["b","3"],"For our exhortation",["i","was"],"not of",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"deceit"],", nor of uncleanness, nor in",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_3b"},"guile"],":"],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/2.4","order":"03.15.002.21453"},["b","4"],"But as we were",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"allowed"],"of God to be",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_4b"},"put"],"in",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_4c"},"trust"],"with the gospel, even so we",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_4d"},"speak"],"; not as",["sup","e"],["a",{"href":"fn_4e"},"pleasing"],"men, but God, which",["sup","f"],["a",{"href":"fn_4f"},"trieth our hearts"],"."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/2.5","order":"03.15.002.21454"},["b","5"],"For neither at any time used we",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"flattering"],"words, as ye know, nor a cloak of",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_5b"},"covetousness"],"; God",["i","is"],"witness:"],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/2.6","order":"03.15.002.21455"},["b","6"],"Nor of men sought we",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"glory"],", neither of you, nor",["i","yet"],"of others, when we might have been burdensome, as the apostles of Christ."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/2.7","order":"03.15.002.21456"},["b","7"],"But we were gentle among you, even as a nurse cherisheth her children:"],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/2.8","order":"03.15.002.21457"},["b","8"],"So being affectionately desirous of you, we were willing to have imparted unto you, not the gospel of God only, but also our own",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"souls"],", because ye were dear unto us."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/2.9","order":"03.15.002.21458"},["b","9"],"For ye remember, brethren, our labour and",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"travail"],": for",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_9b"},"labouring"],"night and day, because we would not be",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_9c"},"chargeable"],"unto any of you, we preached unto you the gospel of God."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/2.10","order":"03.15.002.21459"},["b","10"],"Ye",["i","are"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"witnesses"],", and God",["i","also,"],"how holily and justly and unblameably we behaved ourselves among you that believe:"],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/2.11","order":"03.15.002.21460"},["b","11"],"As ye know how we exhorted and comforted and charged every one of you, as a father",["i","doth"],"his",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"children"],","],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/2.12","order":"03.15.002.21461"},["b","12"],"That ye would",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_12a"},"walk"],["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_12b"},"worthy"],"of God, who hath called you unto his kingdom and glory."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/2.13","order":"03.15.002.21462"},["b","13"],"For this cause also",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"thank"],"we God without ceasing, because, when ye received the word of God which ye heard of us, ye received",["i","it"],"not",["i","as"],"the word of men, but as it is in truth, the word of God, which effectually worketh also in you that believe."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/2.14","order":"03.15.002.21463"},["b","14"],"For ye, brethren, became",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"followers"],"of the churches of God which in Judæa are in Christ Jesus: for ye also have",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_14b"},"suffered"],"like things of your own countrymen, even as they",["i","have"],"of the Jews:"],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/2.15","order":"03.15.002.21464"},["b","15"],"Who both",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_15a"},"killed"],"the Lord Jesus, and their own prophets, and have persecuted us; and they please not God, and are contrary to all men:"],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/2.16","order":"03.15.002.21465"},["b","16"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_16a"},"Forbidding"],"us to speak to the Gentiles that they might be saved, to fill up their sins",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_16b"},"alway"],": for the wrath is come upon them to the uttermost."],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/2.17","order":"03.15.002.21466"},["b","17"],"But we, brethren, being taken from you for a short time in presence, not in heart, endeavoured the more abundantly to see your",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_17a"},"face"],"with great desire."],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/2.18","order":"03.15.002.21467"},["b","18"],"Wherefore we would have come unto you, even I Paul, once and again; but Satan hindered us."],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/2.19","order":"03.15.002.21468"},["b","19"],"For what",["i","is"],"our hope, or joy, or crown of rejoicing?",["i","Are"],"not even ye in the presence of our Lord Jesus Christ at his",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_19a"},"coming"],"?"],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/2.20","order":"03.15.002.21469"},["b","20"],"For ye are our glory and joy."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/2.1a","order":"03.15.002.21470"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/1.5"},"1 Thes. 1:5"],"."],["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/2.2a","order":"03.15.002.21472"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/16.22.19-24"},"Acts 16:22 (19–24)"],"."],["div",{"id":"2b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/2.2b","order":"03.15.002.21474"},["b","2b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/17.2.2-3"},"Acts 17:2 (2–3)"],"."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/2.3a","order":"03.15.002.21476"},["b","3a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/4.2"},"2 Cor. 4:2"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/7.2"},"7:2"],"."],["div",{"id":"3b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/2.3b","order":"03.15.002.21478"},["b","3b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/guile"},"TG Guile"],"."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/2.4a","order":"03.15.002.21480"},["b","4a"],["span.small","GR"],"approved, found worthy, chosen.",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/2-tim/1.11"},"2 Tim. 1:11"],"."],["div",{"id":"4b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/2.4b","order":"03.15.002.21482"},["b","4b"],["span.small","GR"],"entrusted."],["div",{"id":"4c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/2.4c","order":"03.15.002.21484"},["b","4c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/12.8"},"D&C 12:8"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/124.113"},"124:113"],"."],["div",{"id":"4d","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/2.4d","order":"03.15.002.21486"},["b","4d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/titus/2.1"},"Titus 2:1"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/1-pet/4.11"},"1 Pet. 4:11"],"."],["div",{"id":"4e","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/2.4e","order":"03.15.002.21488"},["b","4e"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/peer-influence"},"TG Peer Influence"],"."],["div",{"id":"4f","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/2.4f","order":"03.15.002.21490"},["b","4f"],["span.small","GR"],"examines, proves by trial.",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/test"},"TG Test"],"."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/2.5a","order":"03.15.002.21492"},["b","5a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/flatter"},"TG Flatter"],"."],["div",{"id":"5b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/2.5b","order":"03.15.002.21494"},["b","5b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/covet"},"TG Covet"],"."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/2.6a","order":"03.15.002.21496"},["b","6a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/john/5.44.41-44"},"John 5:44 (41–44)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/76.61"},"D&C 76:61"],"."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/2.8a","order":"03.15.002.21498"},["b","8a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/philip/2.17"},"Philip. 2:17"],"."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/2.9a","order":"03.15.002.21500"},["b","9a"],["span.small","GR"],"toil."],["div",{"id":"9b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/2.9b","order":"03.15.002.21502"},["b","9b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/18.3"},"Acts 18:3"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/20.34"},"20:34"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/work-value-of"},"TG Work, Value of"],"."],["div",{"id":"9c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/2.9c","order":"03.15.002.21504"},["b","9c"],["span.small","GR"],"burdensome.",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/9.18.4-18"},"1 Cor. 9:18 (4–18)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/11.9"},"2 Cor. 11:9"],"."],["div",{"id":"10a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/2.10a","order":"03.15.002.21506"},["b","10a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/1.5"},"1 Thes. 1:5"],"."],["div",{"id":"11a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/2.11a","order":"03.15.002.21508"},["b","11a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/4.14"},"1 Cor. 4:14"],"."],["div",{"id":"12a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/2.12a","order":"03.15.002.21510"},["b","12a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/walking-with-god"},"TG Walking with God"],"."],["div",{"id":"12b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/2.12b","order":"03.15.002.21512"},["b","12b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/1-pet/1.15.15-16"},"1 Pet. 1:15 (15–16)"],"."],["div",{"id":"13a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/2.13a","order":"03.15.002.21514"},["b","13a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/thanksgiving"},"TG Thanksgiving"],"."],["div",{"id":"14a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/2.14a","order":"03.15.002.21516"},["b","14a"],["span.small","GR"],"imitators."],["div",{"id":"14b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/2.14b","order":"03.15.002.21518"},["b","14b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/17.5.5-7"},"Acts 17:5 (5–7)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/2-thes/1.4.4-5"},"2 Thes. 1:4 (4–5)"],"."],["div",{"id":"15a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/2.15a","order":"03.15.002.21520"},["b","15a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/martyrdom"},"TG Martyrdom"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/prophets-rejection-of"},"Prophets, Rejection of"],"."],["div",{"id":"16a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/2.16a","order":"03.15.002.21522"},["b","16a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/luke/11.52"},"Luke 11:52"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/13.45.45,50"},"Acts 13:45 (45, 50)"],"."],["div",{"id":"16b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/2.16b","order":"03.15.002.21524"},["b","16b"],["span.small","GR"],"always."],["div",{"id":"17a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/2.17a","order":"03.15.002.21526"},["b","17a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/3.10"},"1 Thes. 3:10"],"."],["div",{"id":"19a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/2.19a","order":"03.15.002.21528"},["b","19a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/3.13"},"1 Thes. 3:13"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rev/1.7"},"Rev. 1:7"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rev/